Subject: Info from Mark Baldwin re storage issues
Mime-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=us-ascii
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 7bit
X-From: MBD <MDay@GMSSR.com>
X-To: Jeff Dasovich
